  "description": "Aggregate HRIV usage analytics for decision makers, built from structured usage/auth logs in Loki. All panels are aggregate-only: no named-user panels are provisioned (see the 'Privacy & scope' panel). Synthetic-monitor traffic is excluded via the server-marked synthetic flag.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 300,
      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "## HRIV Usage and Experience\n\nAggregate usage analytics from structured logs (Loki). **No named-user panels are provisioned** because Grafana dashboard provisioning is broadly readable. Per-user investigation remains an ad-hoc, access-controlled log workflow.\n\nSynthetic-monitor journeys are excluded everywhere via the server-marked `event_synthetic` / `auth_synthetic` fields. The **User role** variable filters usage-event panels; authentication panels stay aggregate because some failure paths do not carry a resolved role.\n\n> Field names assume OTLP→Loki ingestion, which sanitizes attribute dots to underscores (for example `event.name` → `event_name`).\n\nThe standard **Namespace** and **Application version** variables are carried here for cross-dashboard consistency. Current usage queries stick to dimensions that are exported consistently across the real-user Loki events already in production.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.0.0",
      "title": "Privacy & scope",
      "type": "text",
      "description": "Scope, caveats, and drill-down guidance for this dashboard."
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "${loki}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "blue",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "noValue": "No matching activity"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 4,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.0.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "${loki}"
          },
          "expr": "count(sum by (user_id) (count_over_time({service_name=~\"${component}\"} | event_name=~\"navigation.page_changed|image.view.ready\" | event_synthetic!=\"true\" | user_role=~\"${user_role}\" [$__range])))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Active users",
      "type": "stat",
      "description": "Distinct authenticated users who generated page-view or image-ready events in the selected period."
    },
